\f60\fs24\lang1051\langfe255\langnp1051\insrsid16470304\charrsid16740855 \'af iste by si zatriasol n}{\f2\fs24\lang1051\langfe255\langnp1051\insrsid16470304\charrsid16740855 \'e1h\'beadom o v\'9aemoh\'facnosti nesmiernej sily, \'e8o srdce \'beudsk\'e9 tu
