 nul. Niet bohatstva, moci, ani sl}{\f2\fs24\lang1051\langfe255\langnp1051\insrsid16470304\charrsid16740855 \'e1vy, niet nijak\'fdch v\'fdhod \'9eivota, ktor\'e9 by neprev\'e1\'9eily aspo\'f2 po rovnov\'e1hu i nev\'fdhody, tr\'e1penia a staros\'9d
